porise.model.algorithms.cmab.NeuralUCB.default_prediction¶

NeuralUCB.default_prediction()¶
Might be Used when user features not ready. Due to the following reasons

    1. Large delay to get the features from database

    1. Users features doesn’t exist in the database

By default, return the global mean of all ratings (can be overridden in child classes). Returns:

(float): The mean of all ratings in the trainset.
